metadata.name: Girl with Hat
metadata.description:
In the journey of life, a person sometimes gets sad in life and sometimes smiles. Although Meryem Beyza face expression looks a little sad in this portrait photo she looks to the future with hope. l took her portrait on The Galata bridge which is a great bridge that spans the Golden Horn in Istanbul.

Camera: Canon 5D Mark III
Lens: Canon 24-75 mm f2.8 II
Dimensions: 3840 ×  5760
Resolution: 300 dpi
Location: İstanbul, Turkey
Date: 24/01/2022
Edition: 1 of 1
